  "detailsHtml": "<youtube src=\"https://youtu.be/hlBtknFhRho\"></youtube>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2\">\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-4 relative\">\n      <h1 class=\"text-[16px] font-bold pb-1\">\n        “Absurd Pattern”, 2022, 60mins, live performance, and installation\n      </h1>\n      <p>It's just a process\n      <p>Over time</p>\n      <p>It's changing every second</p>\n      <p>Trapped, Tired, Distressed, Relaxed, Calm, Graceful, Peaceful</p>\n      <p>Transformation is another form of flow</p>\n      <p>Comatose state, Relaxed state, Death rattle, Unconscious state</p>\n      <p>The time comes to a standstill</p>\n\n      <p>它只是一個過程</p>\n      <p>隨著時間的推移</p>\n      <p>它每分每秒都在轉變</p>\n      <p>被困、疲倦、痛苦、放鬆、平靜、輕盈、平和</p>\n      <p>轉變是另一種流動的形態</p>\n      <p>昏迷狀態、放鬆狀態、垂死掙扎、無意識狀態</p>\n      <p>時間進入靜止狀態</p>\n      <p class=\"absolute bottom-1 right-1\">Photo by Thisby Cheung</p>\n    </div>\n    <slider \n      class=\"aspect-[9/16]\" \n      images=\"/images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_1.jpg,\n              /images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_2.jpg,\n              /images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_3.jpg,\n              /images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_4.jpg\" ></slider>\n</div>\n  <slider \n    class=\"aspect-[16/9]\" \n    images=\"/images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_5.jpg,\n            /images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_6.jpg,\n            /images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_7.jpg,\n            /images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_8.jpg,\n            /images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_9.jpg,\n            /images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_10.jpg,\n            /images/uploads/2022_2_the_squirm_motion_11.jpg\" ></slider>",
